Greetings everyone!<BR><BR>

On Wednesday August 30th, we will be conducting maintenance on our Chat and Log-In server from 8 AM to 12 PM PST (11 AM to 3 PM EST). Unfortunately, you will not be able to log into EverQuest during this period, but if you are already logged-in and playing on a server, you will be able to continue playing as long as you do not exit the Character Select Screen.<BR><BR>

We apologize for the inconvenience.<BR><BR>

Thank you,<BR>
